{
    "id": "103",
    "title": "Tokyo Guidelines for Acute Cholecystitis 2018",
    "desc": "The Tokyo Guidelines for Diagnosis and Severity Grading of Acute Cholecystitis provides diagnostic criteria and severity grading for acute cholecystitis.",
